name: MSG Reader
tagline: Outlook Item File (.msg) reader in JavaScript
body:
### MSG Reader
MSG Reader is an Outlook Item File (.msg) reader that is built with HTML5. 

Allows to parse and extract necessary information (attachment included) from .msg file. 

### Online demo
[http://ykarpovich.github.io/msg.reader/examples/example.html](http://ykarpovich.github.io/msg.reader/examples/example.html)
